Clean-room policy
=================

CodeNexus is a clean-room reimplementation of GitNexus concepts.
GitNexus is licensed under PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0 and its source
code has NOT been copied into this project. Design notes were written
from concept understanding without reference to GitNexus source code.
See docs/origin-spec.md for the original Stitch proposal documenting
this clean-room separation.
